- provide(:title, 'Get Involved')
%section#promo.section.alt
  .container
    .hero-unit
      %h1 Get Involved

%section.section#getinvolved
  .container
    .page-header
      %h2
        We think you're kind of a big deal,
        %small and we wanna help get the word out!
    .row-fluid
      %ul.thumbnails.bordered
        %li.span6
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $9
            .span8
              %h3 Post an Idea & Get Listed
              %p
                We want to get you involved! Post an idea, leave the dates TBA, upload a few images, and we'll notify you when someone wants to work with you!
                %br
              = link_to "Post an Idea", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $0
            .span8
              %h3 Pre-register with a Maker
              %p
                Let a maker know that you're interested in working with them by joining their guild. You'll be the first to know when they schedule an event.
                %br
              = link_to "Browse Makers", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center.commingsoon
                .kristi $0
                .commingsoon-text Comming Soon!
            .span8
              %h3 Do a Studio Visit
              %p
                There's no better way to create and refine your own opinions than by talking about them with smart people. Request or host a studio visit with someone you respect in the community.
              = link_to "Register", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success disabled"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi.small $ Varies
            .span8
              %h3 Take a Workshop
              %p
                Play with new materials and techniques, or refine your already awesome skills by taking a workshop taught by someone who's work you love.
                %br
              = link_to "Browse Workshops", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi.small Earn $
            .span8
              %h3 Host a Workshop
              %p
                Play with new materials and techniques, or refine your already awesome skills by taking a workshop taught by someone who's work you love.
                %br
              = link_to "Build a Workshop", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
              %br


        %li.span6
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $9
            .span8
              %h3 Host an Apprenticeship
              %p
                Stuck with a huge order an event, or just need help with your day-to-day practice? Find the help you need by posting an apprenticeship!
                %br
              = link_to "Build an Apprenticeship", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $29
            .span8
              %h3 Do an Event Apprenticeship
              %p
                Help a maker out with organizing, running, curating, or facilitating an event! Learn first hand what it takes to hang a show, or organize a gala.
                %br
              = link_to "Browse Apprenticeships", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $29
            .span8
              %h3 Do a Production Apprenticeship
              %p
                Learn the skills, tools, and techniques unique to the artist's creative process while helping a maker create an edition of her work for an order, a sale, or a show.
              = link_to "Browse Apprenticeships", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center
                .kristi $29
            .span8
              %h3 Do an Ongoing Apprenticeship
              %p
                Work with a creative by assisting her with her day-to-day studio tasks. Help her create work and learn what it's like to own and operate a small creative business.
              = link_to "Browse Apprenticeships", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success"
          %hr/
          .row-fluid
            .span4.pull-center
              %i.enormous-icon.circled.pull-center.commingsoon
                .kristi $45
                .commingsoon-text Comming Soon!
            .span8
              %h3 Do a 1-Day Apprenticeship
              %p
                Get a taste of what it's like to be a carpenter, a web developer, a painter, or a baker, by signing up for a 1-Day Apprenticeship!
                %br
              = link_to "Browse Apprenticeships", apprenticeships_path, class: "btn btn-small pull-right btn-success disabled"


